AnnotationAssertion(Annotation(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasDbXref> <https://explorer.natureserve.org/Taxon/ELEMENT_GLOBAL.2.1299006/Marsh_Wet_Meadow_Shrub_Wetland_Ecobiome>) <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3620279> "An emergent open wetland ecosystem characterised by seasonally to permanently waterlogged soils supporting a continuous cover of herbaceous marsh plants, wet meadow grasses and sedges, or low wetland shrubs."@en)
